  {
   "start": 0.43,
   "end": 6.97,
   "text": "Good morning. This video is comparing African versus European religious statistics."
  },
  {
   "start": 7.71,
   "end": 18.21,
   "text": "Why am I doing this? I don't know. So here we go. It's from Medicine Online, is who's doing it."
  },
  {
   "start": 18.95,
   "end": 27.33,
   "text": "So let's read off the numbers, eh? Now, as far as Africa, now this is in 1994, so it's the same year that we're doing it."
  },
  {
   "start": 27.33,
   "end": 35.39,
   "text": "Africa has a total of 722 million people, Europe 514, so Africa's a little bit bigger than Europe."
  },
  {
   "start": 35.91,
   "end": 38.11,
   "text": "I don't know what it's at, 20% or something like this."
  },
  {
   "start": 39.01,
   "end": 51.47,
   "text": "So, the number one religion in Africa is Christianity, with 342 million people, 48.6% of the population."
  },
  {
   "start": 52.07,
   "end": 56.49,
   "text": "That's pretty much the same as the world, really representative of the world."
  },
  {
   "start": 57.33,
   "end": 61.73,
   "text": "And then you have Islam, is the second most popular religion of Africa."
  },
  {
   "start": 65.11,
   "end": 68.89,
   "text": "Now, here I'll put this so it doesn't move around and give somebody vertigo."
  },
  {
   "start": 70.33,
   "end": 72.11,
   "text": "Let's see if I can use this thing to stand up."
  },
  {
   "start": 73.51,
   "end": 74.51,
   "text": "There we go."
  },
  {
   "start": 74.51,
   "end": 82.73,
   "text": "Now, Native Tribal Religions is the third, with 69,000, 9.6%."
  },
  {
   "start": 82.73,
   "end": 87.25,
   "text": "Non-Religion is the fourth, with almost 3 million people."
  },
  {
   "start": 88.05,
   "end": 90.55,
   "text": "And then Baha'I and Hinduism in sixth."
  },
  {
   "start": 90.61,
   "end": 93.95,
   "text": "That's interesting. I didn't know that those ones from India are in Africa."
  },
  {
   "start": 93.95,
   "end": 99.01,
   "text": "Maybe it's the countries, the oil countries there on the eastern side, like Oman."
  },
  {
   "start": 99.79,
   "end": 102.63,
   "text": "The seventh most popular is others, Taoism is all that stream and stuff."
  },
  {
   "start": 102.73,
   "end": 108.19,
   "text": "And then Atheism, Judaism, Jainism in 10th, 11th Buddhism."
  },
  {
   "start": 108.47,
   "end": 112.31,
